article.headline: Marist 63, Colgate 47
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. (AP) -- Will Whittington scored 15 points, and Ryan Stilphen and Wilfred Benjamin added 12 each as Marist beat Colgate 63-47 on Saturday night. James Smith grabbed 11 rebounds for the Red Foxes (21-7), who shot 42 percent for the game and led 31-27 at halftime. Jon Simon led the Raiders (9-17) with 10 points. Daniel Waddy had 9 points and 7 rebounds.
